# Medical Intake Survey
# Patient information and medical history intake form

> start "Welcome to Medical Intake" "Please complete this medical intake form. Your information is confidential and will be used solely for medical purposes. All data is protected under HIPAA regulations." -> q1

? q1 Tx* "Full name" {placeholder: "Enter your full legal name", minLength: 2, errorMessage: "Please enter your full name"} -> q2

? q2 Dt* "Date of birth" {placeholder: "MM/DD/YYYY", dateFormat: "MM/dd/yyyy", maxDate: "today"} -> q3

? q3 Ch* "Gender" [male="Male", female="Female", other="Other", prefer-not-to-say="Prefer not to say"] -> q4

? q4 Ph* "Contact number" {countryCode: "US", placeholder: "(555) 123-4567"} -> q5

? q5 Yn* "Do you have any allergies?" -> q5a ?= yes
? q5 Yn* "Do you have any allergies?" -> q6

? q5a Mc* "Select allergies" "Please select all that apply" [penicillin="Penicillin", latex="Latex", peanuts="Peanuts", shellfish="Shellfish", other="Other"] {searchable: true} -> q6

? q6 Yn* "Currently on medication?" -> q6a ?= yes
? q6 Yn* "Currently on medication?" -> q7

? q6a Tx* "List medications" "Please list all current medications including dosage" {placeholder: "e.g., Aspirin 81mg daily, Lisinopril 10mg daily", minLength: 3, errorMessage: "Please provide medication details"} -> q7

? q7 Mc* "Reason for visit" "Select all that apply" [checkup="Checkup", follow-up="Follow-up", new-symptoms="New symptoms", other="Other"] -> q8

? q8 Tx "Additional notes" "Any additional information we should know?" {placeholder: "Optional: Provide any additional details about your visit or medical history"} -> end

< end "Thank You" "Your medical intake form has been submitted successfully. A healthcare professional will review your information and contact you shortly."
